This paper discusses the impact of developers on software development, which falls under the category of software engineering (cs.SE). The study involves analyzing data from open source projects, which could also fall under the categories of cybernetics (cs.CY) and social and information networks (cs.SI). The paper also discusses the effects of heroes on software quality, which could fall under programming languages (cs.PL) and machine learning (cs.LG) as these fields also deal with improving software quality.
